entity.name: Humberto strengthens into a Category 3 hurricane
entity.description: Humberto has been given major hurricane status and is causing sustained winds of 115mph (185kph). The system lashed already-devastated parts of the Bahamas with heavy rain and strong winds on the weekend, while Bermuda is expected to be affected on Wednesday and Thursday.

tweets.text: Finally, a low pressure area over the tropical Atlantic is expected to become a tropical depression within the next 24 hours. Follow the latest on all these systems at https://t.co/tW4KeFW0gB https://t.co/QaXpzE3J2V

entity.description: Post-tropical cyclone Dorian, which has already damaged or destroyed thousands of homes in the Bahamas and claimed at least 43 lives, made landfall near Halifax on Saturday evening.

tweets.text: @jwhittalTWN Please do not downplay #HurricaneMichael with the atrocity of #HurricaneDorian. The people of Mexico Beach and the panhandle are still very much in need. Please choose your words better. Please do not override one tragedy with the newer, “worse” tragedy. Praying for the Bahamas.
